<<<BOUNCE Clearing>>>
1> SCRIPT LOCATION 
/home/arpit/script/bounce_clear.sh

2>Argument to pass to the script
	Datafile to clear the bounce data from
	
3> Nature of script
. This script will get data file as input.
. This script with help of sed will list all bounce mailids from bounce file and will dlete it from datafile all at once.
. same operation will be carried out for other isps
. Latter with the difference in line count of datafile before and after sed command , get the number of bounce data cleared from that file for respectiv isp

SAMPLE OUTPUT
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
